data.title: 以 3 到 5 分钟描写以下主题
data.content: Describe a memorable place that you only visited once in your life. Why is that place so memorable? Do you think it would be as memorable to other people?
data.answer: Bondi Beach is a very popular place for people in Sydney to go for swimming and other recreational activities. I visited this famous beach in 2007 when I first came to Australia with my family. It was a very memorable and exciting trip for me because we do not really have many beautiful beaches and seaside places in my hometown. The whole experience was new for me, and I absolutely loved it! I guess this place also leaves a long-lasting memory for people whoever visited it because there are a lot of excellent bars and cafes around the beach. （99 字）
